<span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-36pt"><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">1.</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">3</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">  </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">It has become apparent that cycling as a mode of transport is on the increase as more road users </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">are</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt"> switching </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">to pedal cycle</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">s. This has been enhanced with the success of the British Cycling </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">T</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">eam and </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">as a more cost effective, sometimes quicker and greener way to comm</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">ute to work and places of </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">study</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-36pt"><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-36pt"><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">1.4</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">Greater Manchester is the home of British Cycling and has excellent faciliti</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">es within the </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">Velodrome</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">. The </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">road</span><s