e third being </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">road safety presentations with the offer of free</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt"> cycle training.  </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">3</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">. </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">              </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:14pt; text-decoration:underline">Walkthrough</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-36pt"><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">3</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">.1  </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">Initially </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">Operation ‘</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">Grimaldi</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">’ staff </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt"> arrange a suitable place to</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt"> hold an interactive walk through in specifically targeted areas</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt"> such as town </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">centre’s</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt"> or outside </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">the </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">University buildings. This involves </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">vehicles from a </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">local haulage </span><span sty