:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-36pt"><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">8.2</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">Cycle retailers could do more to support the work of the local authorities, police and community groups by ensuring </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">when </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">they sell a cycle </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">it is </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">fitted with the </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">respective lighting</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">, security</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">, (lock and cycle marking</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">) fluorescent</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt"> jacket</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt"> and </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">advice on the rules of the road for cyclists</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">, cycle maintenance </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">together with</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt"> free cycling information</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt"> in with the purchase price.</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-36pt"><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">8.3</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">An N</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">DORS style</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:1